headline: Morgan Stanley Recruits Advisor Team With $775 Million From Merrill Lynch
summary: BEST PRACTICES  Morgan Stanley Wealth Management has recruited an advisor team with more than $775 million in client assets from rival Merrill Lynch.  The five-member team, known as the Fischer Group, is led by advisors Billy Fischer and Jean Pierre “JP” Lemoine.
